### 5. automation/deployment-checklist.md
```markdown
# Automated Deployment Checklist

## Pre-Launch
- [ ] Domain purchased and configured
- [ ] SSL certificate installed
- [ ] Database schema deployed
- [ ] Environment variables configured
- [ ] Payment system tested
- [ ] Email automation setup
- [ ] Analytics tracking installed
- [ ] Backup procedures configured

## Launch Day
- [ ] Final code push
- [ ] Database migrations run
- [ ] Payment system activated
- [ ] Email sequences activated  
- [ ] Social media posts scheduled
- [ ] Monitoring alerts configured
- [ ] Customer support system ready

## Post-Launch
- [ ] Monitor for errors (24h)
- [ ] Check payment processing
- [ ] Verify email delivery
- [ ] Monitor user registrations
- [ ] Track conversion rates
- [ ] Collect initial feedback
- [ ] Document lessons learned
```

## Implementation Instructions

1. **Create these files in order:**
   - Start with README.md in root
   - Create the folder structure
   - Add the template files
   - Customize for your specific needs

2. **Voice-Friendly Approach:**
   - Create one file at a time
   - Use voice-to-text for content
   - Copy-paste templates when possible
   - Iterate and improve over time

3. **Priority Order:**
   1. README.md (root)
   2. docs/development-process.md  
   3. First project folder
   4. AI conversation logs
   5. Templates and automation

This structure will grow with you from beach bootstrapping to full home lab automation!
